<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.1">
<l>eṭṭi yilava mīkai cūrai kārai paṭarnteṅkuñ</l>
<l>cuṭṭa cuṭalai cūḻnta kaḷḷi cōrnta kuṭarkauvap</l>
<l>paṭṭa piṇaṅkaḷ paranta kāṭṭiṟ paṟaipōl viḻikaṭpēy</l>
<l>koṭṭa muḻavaṅ kūḷi pāṭak kuḻaka ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wherever strychnine, silk cotton, mimosa, night-shade and thorn bushes spread,</l>
<l>while Euphorbia, that surrounds the burned-out pyre, grips spilled intestines,</l>
<l>while in the cremation ground spread with fallen corpses the demonesses,</l>
<l>eyes wide open like drums, beat drums, while demons sing the young one is dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
